=== closure value ===
allocation certificate `without alloc` failed for function `make`: allocates a fresh closure (no reuse token available)
witness: a lambda/thunk value must be materialized as a closure cell; call a named function directly or move the lambda outside the zero-allocation region
=== explicit fbip allocation ===
usage check `fbip` failed for function `fresh`: allocates a fresh `Box` (no reuse token available)
witness: `Box` is constructed outside `reuse`, so it calls the allocator instead of spending a freed cell
